Package org.apache.log4j.chainsaw

Interface ChainsawReceiver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChainsawReceiverSkeleton, Generator, JsonReceiver, LogFilePatternReceiver, LogFileXMLReceiver, MulticastReceiver, UDPReceiver, VFSLogFilePatternReceiver, XMLSocketReceiver
    public interface ChainsawReceiver
    A receiver receives log events from a source. A ChainsawReceiver will create from 1...N ChainsawReceiverNodes
